---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Martin Justin | Home">
  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="profile-header">
      <div class="header-info">
        <h1 class="author-name">Martin<br />Justin</h1>
        <p class="author-role">PhD Student in Philosophy<br />University of Maribor</p>
      </div>
      <div class="portrait-container">
        <img src="/avatar.jpg" alt="Martin Justin" class="portrait-image" />
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bio-content">
      <p>
        I’m a PhD student at the University of Maribor, Slovenia. My research interests are in philosophy of science and epistemology. Currently, I’m working on higher-order evidence and using computer simulations to study science. Additionally, I act as an editorial assistant at the journal Acta Analytica (Springer).
      </p>
      <p>
        I also work as a freelance writer and editor. From 2023 to 2025, I served as the editor-in-chief at ludliteratura.si. In 2023, I served as a coordinator of the Slovenian Literary Critics’ Association.
      </p>
      <p>
        Feel free to contact me at martin1123581321(at)gmail(dot)com.
      </p>
      
      <div class="links-block font-bold tracking-wide">
        <a href="https://uni-aas.academia.edu/MartinJustin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">[Academia.edu]</a>
        <a href="https://philpeople.org/profiles/martin-justin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">[PhilPeople]</a>
        <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/martinjustin.bsky.social" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">[Bluesky]</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .profile-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .header-info {
    flex: 3;
  }

  .author-name {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin: 0 0 0.8rem 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .author-role {
    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.4;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .portrait-container {
    flex: 7;
  }

  .portrait-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    display: block;
  }

  .bio-content p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .links-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .links-block a {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .links-block a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
